International Paper in North America


















Home| Company| Regions| North America



  Print   













 North America International Paper is headquartered in Memphis, Tennessee, and has been a strong presence in North America for more than a century. Our nearly 34,000 employees in the region work at more than 200 facilities from coast to coast. We are recognized as the premier manufacturer of containerboard and corrugated packaging products, uncoated freesheet papers, coated paperboard, fluff pulp and also deliver innovative single-use packaging to the foodservice industry. 











Businesses
North America is home to International Paper's headquarters in Memphis, Tennessee and several businesses.


















Products
Learn more about International Paper's product offering in North America.


















Community
International Paper serves the community by being an active citizen in a variety of philanthropic efforts.


















Supplier Diversity
Supplier diversity is a value-added strategy that ensures quality products and services to our customers.








  








Careers​
It's time to embrace your Infinite Possibilities. This is your opportunity to be part of International Paper, a Fortune 500 company and global leader in paper and packaging products. 
   











